snippet.title: Viking Squad Launch Trailer ESRB
snippet.description:
Releasing on Steam and PS4 (North America) on October 4th, and PS4 (Europe) on October 5th.
Please visit http://www.vikingsquadgame.com for more info.
Oh and tell your friends! :)
